path = Path(os.path.realpath(__file__), '../../../fixtures/ICL-SandPack(F42A)')
project = op.io.Statoil.load(path=path.resolve(), prefix='F42A')
assert len(project) == 1
net = project.network
assert net.Np == 1246
assert net.Nt == 2654
assert np.shape(net['pore.coords']) == (1246, 3)
assert np.shape(net['throat.conns']) == (2654, 2)
assert 'pore.radius' in net.keys()
